These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
City: miami, rome, liverpool
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, taxi, tram
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, lily, amaryllis
3 different pets are kept: fish, mouse, hamster
3 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, mah-jongg
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, apricot, mauve
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, family, time-travel
 1. the person watching disaster movies is the person who likes apricot##1
 2. the person watching time-travel movies is the owner of the hamster##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person who likes mauve and the person traveling to rome##2
 4. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 5. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the tram##1
 6. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who likes blood-red##1
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 8. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
10. the person who growslily is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| City      | rome    | liverpool   | miami           |
| Transport          | taxi       | tram    | roller         |
| Flower         | lily    | amaryllis  | begonia        |
| Pet           | fish | mouse   | hamster      |
| Game   | backgammon        | mah-jongg    | canasta       |
| Color   | apricot     | blood-red  | mauve       |
| Movie-Genre         | disaster     | family | time-travel |

