 2. the prince-smoker is the photographer##1
 3. the photographer is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 4. the person playing billiard is between the person traveling to hannover and the person traveling to london##2
 5. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
 6. the person traveling to hannover is the wooden house##1
 7. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is the manager##1
 9. the photographer is on the right of the tower house##1
10. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| City      | london   | san-francisco    | hannover         |
| Birthday          | april    | february | july          |
| Job   | manager  | photographer  | nurse     |
