3 different games are played: whist, backgammon, bridge
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, dubstep, blues
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, sunflower, balloon-flower
House: gothic-revival, wooden, craftsman
There 3 different types of food: pear, grapes, tomato
City: paris, liverpool, miami
 1. the person eating tomato is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
 3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 4. the person playing bridge is the fan dubstep##1
 5. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 6. the craftsman house is on the left of the fan dubstep##1
 7. the person traveling to miami is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who growsbellflower##2
 8. the fan funk is on the right of the person eating pear##1
 9. the fan dubstep is the person traveling to paris##1
10. the craftsman house is on the left of the wooden house##1
11. the person traveling to paris is the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday      | april | august      | december      |
| Game         | whist     | backgammon     | bridge  |
| Music-Genre   | blues | funk  | dubstep |
| Flower   | sunflower  | balloon-flower     | bellflower |
| House           | gothic-revival        | craftsman | wooden     |
| Food         | pear    | tomato | grapes   |
| City     | liverpool        | miami        | paris   |

