.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, yellow, white
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, amaryllis, begonia
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, hip-hop, ambient
City: rome, venice, hamburg
3 different pets are kept: rat, blacksy, hamster
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, september, april
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, spanish, polish
1. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the polish is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is between the owner of the rat and the person traveling to venice##2
5. the person who growsbegonia is between the person traveling to hamburg and the fan ambient##2
6. the fan hip-hop is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
8. the brazilian is on the left of the person who likes white##1
9. the owner of the blacksy is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
