The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, zinnia, tulip
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, october, november
3 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, hedgehog
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, coral, aquamarine
1. the person who likes coral is the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
5. the nurse is between the tiparillo-smoker and the person traveling to boston##2
6. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
7. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
8. the person who likes blood-red is the person who growstulip##1
9. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
