.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, backgammon
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, fishing, reading
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, july, september
City: san-francisco, boston, liverpool
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, fonseca, prince
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, techno, d&b
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, yellow, apricot
1. the person playing monopoly is the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who likes apricot is the fan folk##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person playing backgammon and the prince-smoker##2
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
5. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the fan d&b##1
6. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's hobby is chess##1
8. the prince-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
9. the person traveling to boston is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who likes brown##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Game      | billiard    | monopoly       | backgammon      |
| Hobby          | chess   | reading   | fishing  |
| Birthday           | july  | august | september    |
| City   | san-francisco   | boston     | liverpool  |
| Cigar           | prince     | dannemann        | fonseca |
| Music-Genre         | techno | folk   | d&b  |
| Color     | yellow    | apricot     | brown      |

 